@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_admhfl(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = ((wp.exp(v1 + 0.12) / (v0 + 0.61 / v0 + 0.14)) * v0)
    v1 = v2
    v0 = (wp.cos(wp.abs(v1 + 0.57)) + wp.cos(wp.exp(tmp + 0.44)))
    v1 = tmp
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.cos(0.71))
    tmp = 0.45
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.abs((v0 + 0.89 + v0 + 0.64)))
    data[tid] = v0
